    <fr:title text="Inverse image">Inverse image</fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R\colon  A\mathbin {\nrightarrow } B]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="jms-00I7.xml" title="Relation" addr="jms-00I7" type="local">relation</fr:link>. The <fr:em><fr:strong>inverse image</fr:strong></fr:em> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Y\subseteq  B]]></fr:tex> under <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex> is the set <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R^*Y\subseteq  A]]></fr:tex> defined below:</fr:p>
    <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
 R^*Y =
 {\mathopen {}\left \{a\in  A\,\middle \vert \,
  \forall  b\in  B\mathpunct {.}
  a\mathrel {R}b\implies 
  b\in  Y
 \right \}\mathclose {}}
]]></fr:tex>
  </fr:mainmatter>
