                <fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R\colon  A\mathbin {\nrightarrow } B]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="jms-00I7.xml" title="Relation" addr="jms-00I7" type="local">relation</fr:link>. The <fr:em><fr:strong>direct image</fr:strong></fr:em> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X\subseteq  A]]></fr:tex> under <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex> is the set <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R_*X\subseteq  B]]></fr:tex> defined below:</fr:p>
